Prepare sausage according to directions. Cool slightly; cut into 1/4-in. slices. Prepare pasta according to package directions. In a large saucepan, saute the onion and garlic in olive oil until tender. Stir in tomatoes and chicken broth. Bring to a simmer. Add the broccoli and cooked pasta. Cook until broccoli is tender, about 5 minutes. Add sausage; toss to combine.